{"tid":1091783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高空亂棄煙頭應當縱火】政府係咪要等到燒死人先做嘢？","createTime":"2019-04-04T10:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T12:50:31.000Z","uid":70786,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"334560d5b5ceff596c7b586150be645a106ce2f6","tid":1091783,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"兩年前已經開過post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">覺唔覺亂拋煙蒂致起火應當縱火處理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/138230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/138230</a></span><br />\n<br />\n近期一個月內又爆兩單<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">【掉煙頭毀人家】無辜被燒屋 兩子失校服難上學 苦主：一無所有<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1081051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1081051</a><br />\n<br />\n青衣邨缺德住客掉煙頭燒雜物起火 居民自保疏散<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1091706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1091706</a></span><br />\n<br />\n愈嚟愈頻密<br />\n唔知同多咗無公德心嘅支那人同反社會死廢中廢老有冇關係<br />\n但希望政府可以正視問題<br />\n唔好燒死人先做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先要拍廣告作教育宣傳<br />\n喺高危地點裝天眼監察咩單位掉煙頭出街<br />\n於住宅大廈四周巡查，撿拾棄置煙頭拎去化驗DNA（特別係大廈天井／簷篷）<br />\n搜證完上門拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139c9b94bcd6f2ebdc69040c85c474042e7a5260","tid":1091783,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T11:01:45.000Z","msg":"唔係又收隊當冇事下化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於高空擲物可能造成嚴重危險或人身傷害的租戶，房委會會引用《房屋條例》發出遷出通知書，終止其租約。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6547bbf090a7f777c31f6803ad84b77ce9009bef","tid":1091783,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"成日望住鄰居伸隻手出去(等)煙灰<br />\n食完一野彈出去<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他狗屎垃圾都照掉<br />\n<br />\n不過仍然住係度"},{"pid":"bc230dce3f4e12b013c46f57b1cc4f949eced218","tid":1091783,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6547bbf090a7f777c31f6803ad84b77ce9009bef","tid":1091783,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"成日望住鄰居伸隻手出去(等)煙灰<br />\n食完一野彈出去<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他狗屎垃圾都照掉<br />\n<br />\n不過仍然住係度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T11:30:14.000Z","msg":"拍片捕佢再匿名投訴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22339486ef253de9292c16eabb075671ee6bef3f","tid":1091783,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T11:49:18.000Z","msg":"連登咁多人住公屋但冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cda404a64e83902f26175ee7b1ac2dd3ebadbe","tid":1091783,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T11:59:56.000Z","msg":"食煙應該要即刻槍斃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n縱火案又要慢慢審，啲死煙剷分分鐘審審下都cancer死咗"},{"pid":"8b71aece7247444ba37c1a4f829f0e264bbaf37c","tid":1091783,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:14:53.000Z","msg":"8仙嶺都冇事呢d點會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f883d3c268abf8b1c4dee1be6d580b0e396f03ad","tid":1091783,"uid":55032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"樓豬 自私撚  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7914d0f8755cf9d12ed0c91701135e5897cd79b","tid":1091783,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f883d3c268abf8b1c4dee1be6d580b0e396f03ad","tid":1091783,"uid":55032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"樓豬 自私撚  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img sr